channel.title: [PI]Elitescape Devolpment -- 317
channel.description:
Hey guys,
Welcome to our Elitescape Devolpment blog.
What we have achieved so far:
Website wise:
- Webclient - Vps Hosted 24 - 7 - Smf Forums - Domain name
Server Wise:
- Base is Pi if your wondering. - Skillcape Emotes - Skilling area! - Turmoil - Soulsplit pray 100% working like rs. - Kill/death ratio - Dragon Claws only GFX missing. - Armadyl boss working perfectly (only needs kc interface) - Bandos Boss working perfectly (only needs kc interface) - Saradomin Boss working perfectly (only needs kc interface) - Zamorak boss working perfectly (only needs kc interface) - Need 20 KC to enter godwars - Dragon Fireshield Special when operated - 474+ Emotes loaded from cache - 474+ Gfx’s loaded from cache - 474+ interfaces loaded from cache - Almost all specials work - Rune Crossbow (e)’s special effects working like RS - Ice barrage multi freeze - Perfect Barrows(Secret Coffin, Shovel, chest) - Pest Control with correct interfaces and wait timers. - Perfect Combat + master switching system - Amazing Stability - Duel Arena + staking. - King Black Dragon with 474 anims and gfx - All Skills Working! - Amazing fight pits. - Auto Retaliate works - Dark Bow special working perfectly - Awesome Starter - Home is Edgevile. Including Altars/Shops/Slayer/Thieve & More - Ava’s Accumulator working - Slayer tower with 3 floors, and slayer tasks! - Clan Chat with toggeling + deleting clan - PVP drops no pvp system shit. - 100% Working clue scrolls - Toggling for Status orbs on/off - Toggling for new/old Hp bar - Toggling for new/old hitmarks - Toggling for transparent/normal right click menu - Toggling for X10 Hits - Gameframe settings 474, 525, 562. - Private chat color changing - Pk points shop - PVP armour correct ints + model like runescape - Full runescape Clue Scrolls - "Swarm" Custom Minigames - Dungeneering skill Minigame + Runescape rewards - All skills 100%
Pictures: More coming soon:
Swarm Minigame + Working Void!
*
New Home!
*
100% Godwars + chaos prayers!
*
100% Skillcape emotes, Just like Runescape!
*
100% Dueling + Chaotic Weps
*
Thanks,
Will
